Space optimization 
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 6;

        if (n <= 1) {
            System.out.println(n);
            return;
        }

        int prev2 = 0; // fib(0)
        int prev1 = 1; // fib(1)

        for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
            int curr = prev1 + prev2;
            prev2 = prev1;
            prev1 = curr;
        }

        System.out.println(prev1);
    }
}
Time: O(n)
Space: O(1)
